comments: Ayton (PHX) briefly engages with Antetokounmpo (MIL) as they move up the lane for the pick.
Booker (PHX) places a hand to Middleton's (MIL) opposite hip on his drive and affects his SQBR before he is able to reach and dislodge the ball.
Paul (PHX) makes marginal contact to Antetokounmpo's (MIL) arm while defending the pass.
Paul (PHX) fails to get to the height of the ball and makes contact with Antetokounmpo's (MIL) arm that affects his shot near the rim.
Connaughton (MIL) maintains a legal guarding position on Paul's (PHX) drive to the basket and absorbs the oncoming contact on the shot.
Tucker (MIL) is in Booker's (PHX) path before the contact, shifting slightly to absorb the contact in his chest.  Booker bumps into the screen and bounces off without going through Tucker's space.
Paul (PHX) is in a legal guarding position in Middleton's (MIL) path before the contact and Middleton does not go through Paul's space.
Holiday (MIL) strips the ball from Booker (PHX). As Booker turns to expose the ball, there is incidental contact to his arm during the steal, which is not what dislodges the ball.
Paul (PHX) makes contact to Antetokounmpo's (MIL) body while defending his shot attempt at the rim.
Ayton (PHX) enters the lane before Antetokounmpo (MIL) releases the ball on his free throw attempt.
Booker (PHX) makes contact to the body of Middleton (MIL) and dislodges him from his position.
